OL,3,CAshes of up to 300,000 people remain
OL,4,Cunclaimed across the UK, undertakers
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe National Association of Funeral
OL,8,FDirectors (NAFD) has called for a
OL,9,F"workable solution" to respectfully
OL,10,Fdeal with the ashes of up to 300,000
OL,11,Fpeople left unclaimed at funeral
OL,12,Fparlours across the UK.
OL,14,FThe organisation said the large number
OL,15,Fpresents a growing challenge for
OL,16,Ffuneral directors who often struggle
OL,17,Fwith limited storage capacity to hold
OL,18,Fthe ashes long-term.
