OL,3,CAshes of up to 300,000 people remain
OL,4,Cunclaimed across the UK, undertakers
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FAlthough the exact figure is not
OL,8,Fknown, the NAFD estimates between
OL,9,F250,000 and 300,000 sets of ashes
OL,10,Fremain unclaimed.
OL,12,FReasons ashes are not claimed can
OL,13,Fvary, the NAFD said, from family
OL,14,Fdisputes, to illness, or the desire to
OL,15,Fscatter two sets of ashes together.
OL,17,FIn response, the Law Commission has
OL,18,Fbeen reviewing burial and cremation
OL,19,Flaws, proposing reforms that include a
OL,20,Fset deadline for collecting unclaimed
OL,21,Fashes.
