OL,3,CAshes of up to 300,000 people remain
OL,4,Cunclaimed across the UK, undertakers
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FUnder the proposed rules, if the
OL,8,Fapplicant does not respond within four
OL,9,Fweeks, funeral directors could return
OL,10,Fthe ashes to the crematorium, which
OL,11,Fwould then have the authority to
OL,12,Fscatter or bury the ashes.
OL,14,FWhile the NAFD supports the overall
OL,15,Fintention of the Law Commission's
OL,16,Fproposals, it has raised concerns
OL,17,Fabout the proposed four-week deadline
OL,18,Ffor families to collect ashes.
