OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FRachel Bradburne, director of external
OL,8,Faffairs at the NAFD, suggested that
OL,9,Fthis period may be too short and
OL,10,Fadvocated for extending it to at least
OL,11,Feight weeks.
OL,13,F"Changing family patterns, people
OL,14,Fresiding abroad, or illness could
OL,15,Feasily delay this process for longer
OL,16,Fthan a month," Ms. Bradburne explained.
