OL,7,FShe added: "When the wishes are not
OL,8,Fknown we want to find a way to ensure
OL,9,Fthat all the sets of historic remains
OL,10,Fthat are currently sat with funeral
OL,11,Fdirectors can be laid to rest finally,
OL,12,Frespectfully, and in a way that is
OL,13,Freassuring for the wider public."
